Manchester United’s Paul Scholes Retires, Takes Up Coaching Role

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-05-31T08:27:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/manchester-united-s-paul-scholes-retires-takes-up-coaching-role.html
Manchester United midfielder  Paul
Scholes  has retired from playing with immediate effect, the
English soccer champion said on its website. He’ll take up a
coaching role at the club next season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  